50|$|In 2004, the Black Farmers and Agriculturalists Association (BFAA) filed a US$20.5 billion {{class action}} {{lawsuit against the}} USDA for the same {{practices}}, alleging racially discriminatory practices between 1997 and 2004. The lawsuit was dismissed when the BFAA failed to show it had standing <b>to</b> <b>bring</b> the <b>suit.</b>|$|R
